    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Trim, then chop the <strong>spring onions</strong> into large pieces</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-basa-and-pea-risotto-with-poached-egg/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped spring onion</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until it's softened slightly</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-basa-and-pea-risotto-with-poached-egg/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 700ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-basa-and-pea-risotto-with-poached-egg/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the<strong> </strong>spring onion has softened, add the <strong>arborio rice</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in oil</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-basa-and-pea-risotto-with-poached-egg/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-basa-and-pea-risotto-with-poached-egg/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the<strong> smoked basa fillets</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once the rice is almost cooked, add the<strong> blanched peas</strong>,<strong> grated cheese</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>smoked basa</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-6 min or until the fish is cooked through and the peas are tender \u2013 this is your <strong>smoked basa & pea risotto</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p><p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> chives </strong>finely</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-basa-and-pea-risotto-with-poached-egg/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Bring a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Crack the<strong> eggs </strong>gently into the water and leave them for 3 min</p><p>Once done, gently transfer the <strong>eggs</strong> with a slotted spoon to<strong> </strong>kitchen paper or a clean tea-towel and season them with<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> \u2013 these are your <strong>poached eggs</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-basa-and-pea-risotto-with-poached-egg/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>poached egg</strong> over the <strong>smoked basa & pea risotto</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chives</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
